[
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛說佛母出生三法藏般若",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0604a06_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "波羅蜜多經卷第五",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0604a07_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "西天譯經三藏朝奉大夫試光祿卿",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0604a09_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "傳法大師賜紫臣施護奉　詔譯",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0604a10_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "正福品第五之二",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0604a11_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，憍尸迦！",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0604a12_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若善男子、善女人，以滿閻浮提所有眾生，各各教令修四禪定。",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0604a12_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "憍尸迦！",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0604a13_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於汝意云何，彼人以是因緣得福多不？」",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0604a13_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "帝釋天主白佛言：「甚多，世尊！」",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0604a14_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛言：「憍尸迦！",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0604a15_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是善男子、善女人，以是因緣得福雖多，不如有人於此般若波羅蜜多，發信解心、發菩提心住菩薩法，以此般若波羅蜜多，書寫經卷受持讀誦，生歡喜心為人演說，或復為人解釋其義，於此正法生清淨心離諸疑惑，轉勸他人使其受持，作如是言：『汝善男子！",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0604a15_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此般若波羅蜜多是菩薩道，汝於是中如所宣說應當修學。",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0604a21_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是學者乃名得法，即能速證阿耨多羅三藐三菩提，能盡一切諸有情界，普令安住真如實際。』",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0604a22_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "憍尸迦！",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0604a25_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是善男子、善女人得福甚多。",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0604a25_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，憍尸迦！",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0604a26_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "置是滿閻浮提所有眾生。",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0604a26_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若滿四大洲所有眾生，各各教令修四禪定，復置是數；若滿小千世界所有眾生，各各教令修四禪定，亦置是數；若滿中千世界所有眾生，各各教令修四禪定，亦置是數；若滿三千大千世界所有眾生，各各教令修四禪定，亦置是數；如是乃至若滿兢伽沙數三千大千世界所有眾生，一一教令修四禪定。",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0604a26_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "憍尸迦！",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0604b05_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於汝意云何，彼人以是因緣得福多不？」",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0604b05_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "帝釋天主白佛言：「甚多，世尊！」",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0604b06_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛言：「憍尸迦！",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0604b07_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是善男子、善女人，以是因緣得福雖多，不如有人於此般若波羅蜜多，發信解心、發菩提心住菩薩法，以此般若波羅蜜多，書寫經卷受持讀誦，生歡喜心為人演說，或復為人解釋其義，於此正法生清淨心離諸疑惑，轉勸他人使其受持，作如是言：『汝善男子！",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0604b07_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此般若波羅蜜多是菩薩道，汝於是中如所宣說應當修學。",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0604b13_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是學者乃名得法，即能速證阿耨多羅三藐三菩提，能盡一切諸有情界，普令安住真如實際。』",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0604b14_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "憍尸迦！",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0604b17_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當知是人得福甚多。",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0604b17_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，憍尸迦！",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0604b17_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若滿閻浮提所有眾生，各各教修四無量行、四無色定，乃至普修一切神通梵行諸禪定法及諸福行。",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0604b18_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "憍尸迦！",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0604b20_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於汝意云何，彼人以是因緣得福多不？」",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0604b20_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "帝釋天主白佛言：「甚多，世尊！」",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0604b21_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛言：「憍尸迦！",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0604b22_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是善男子、善女人，以是因緣得福雖多，不如有人於此般若波羅蜜多，發信解心、發菩提心住菩薩法，以此般若波羅蜜多，書寫經卷受持讀誦，生歡喜心為人演說，或復為人解釋其義，於此正法生清淨心離諸疑惑，轉勸他人使其受持，作如是言：『汝善男子！",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0604b22_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此般若波羅蜜多是菩薩道，汝於是中如所宣說應當修學。",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0604b28_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是學者乃名得法，即能速證阿耨多羅三藐三菩提，能盡一切諸有情界，普令安住真如實際。』",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0604b29_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "憍尸迦！",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0604c02_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是善男子、善女人得福甚多。",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0604c02_22",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，憍尸迦！",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0604c04_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "置是滿閻浮提所有眾生，各各教修無量無邊神通梵行諸禪定法及諸福行。",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0604c04_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "憍尸迦！",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0604c06_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若滿四大洲、若滿小千世界、若滿中千世界、若滿三千大千世界所有眾生，各各教修無量無邊神通梵行諸禪定法及諸福行。",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0604c06_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一一皆置是數，憍尸迦！",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0604c09_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "假使若滿兢伽沙數三千大千世界所有眾生，各各教修無量無邊神通梵行諸禪定法及諸福行。",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0604c09_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "憍尸迦！",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0604c11_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於汝意云何，是人以是因緣得福多不？」",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0604c12_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "帝釋天主白佛言：「甚多，世尊！」",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0604c12_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛言：「憍尸迦！",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0604c13_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是善男子、善女人，以是因緣得福雖多，不如有人於此般若波羅蜜多，發信解心、發菩提心住菩薩法，以此般若波羅蜜多，書寫經卷受持讀誦，生歡喜心為人演說，或復為人解釋其義，於此正法生清淨心離諸疑惑，轉勸他人使其受持，作如是言：『汝善男子！",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0604c13_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此般若波羅蜜多是菩薩道，汝於是中如所宣說應當修學。",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0604c19_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是學者乃名得法，即能速證阿耨多羅三藐三菩提，能盡一切諸有情界，普令安住真如實際。』",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0604c21_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "憍尸迦！",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0604c23_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是善男子、善女人得福甚多。",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0604c23_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，憍尸迦！",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0604c25_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若善男子、善女人，以此般若波羅蜜多書寫經卷，自當受持讀誦，轉勸他人使其讀誦，得福雖多。",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0604c25_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不如有人以此般若波羅蜜多法門，廣為他人解釋其義。",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0604c27_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "憍尸迦！",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0604c28_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當知是善男子、善女人得福甚多。」",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0604c28_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，帝釋天主白佛言：「世尊！",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0605a01_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當為何等人解說此般若波羅蜜多？」",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0605a01_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛告帝釋天主言：「若有善男子、善女人，於此般若波羅蜜多不能了知者，當為彼說。",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0605a02_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0605a04_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "憍尸迦！",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0605a04_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "未來世中當有人說相似般若波羅蜜多。",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0605a04_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若有善男子、善女人，為欲趣證阿耨多羅三藐三菩提者，聞是相似般若波羅蜜多於中學者、則為錯亂，非正了知。」",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0605a05_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "帝釋天主白佛言：「世尊！",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0605a08_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "未來世中，云何說彼相似般若波羅蜜多？",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0605a08_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又復云何悉能辯了？」",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0605a09_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛告帝釋天主言：「憍尸迦！",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0605a10_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "未來世中有諸苾芻，作如是說：『色是無常，若身若心及戒定慧，悉無所有，離諸所觀。』",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0605a10_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "作是說者，當知是說相似般若波羅蜜多。",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0605a12_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "憍尸迦！",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0605a13_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何名為相似般若波羅蜜多？",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0605a13_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼作是說：『壞色故觀色無常，壞受、想、行、識故觀受、想、行、識無常，若如是求，是為行般若波羅蜜多。』",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0605a14_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "憍尸迦！",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0605a16_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當知此說皆得名為相似般若波羅蜜多。",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0605a16_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "憍尸迦！",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0605a17_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝今當知，不壞色故觀色無常，不壞受、想、行、識故觀受想行識無常。",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0605a17_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "作是說者，是為如實宣說般若波羅蜜多。",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0605a19_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "憍尸迦！",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0605a20_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以是義故，若善男子、善女人，能為他人如實解說般若波羅蜜多義者，當知是善男子、善女人得福甚多。",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0605a20_22",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，憍尸迦！",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0605a23_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若善男子、善女人，以滿閻浮提所有眾生，普令安住須陀洹果。",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0605a23_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "憍尸迦！",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0605a24_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於汝意云何，是善男子、善女人，以是因緣得福多不？」",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0605a24_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "帝釋天主白佛言：「甚多，世尊！」",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0605a26_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛言：「憍尸迦！",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0605a26_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是善男子、善女人，以是因緣得福雖多，不如有人於此般若波羅蜜多，發信解心、發菩提心住菩薩法，以此般若波羅蜜多，書寫經卷受持讀誦，生歡喜心為人演說，或復為人解釋其義，於此正法生清淨心離諸疑惑，轉勸他人使其受持，作如是言：『汝善男子！",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0605a27_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此般若波羅蜜多是菩薩道，汝於是中如所宣說應當修學。",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0605b03_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是學者乃名得法，即能速證阿耨多羅三藐三菩提，能盡一切諸有情界，普令安住真如實際。』",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0605b05_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
