        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故所有須陀洹、斯陀含、阿那含、阿羅漢、緣覺，及彼如來、應供、正等正覺，皆悉從是般若波羅蜜多出生。",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0606c03_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如所出生，如理而得。",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0606c05_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「憍尸迦！",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0606c05_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如前所說，若人以滿閻浮提所有眾生，普令安住阿羅漢果，且置是數。",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0606c06_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "假使若滿四大洲、若滿小千世界、若滿中千世界、若滿三千大千世界所有眾生，普令安住阿羅漢果，皆置是數。",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0606c07_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "憍尸迦！",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0606c10_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "假使若滿兢伽沙數三千大千世界所有眾生，普令安住阿羅漢果。",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0606c10_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "憍尸迦！",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0606c12_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於汝意云何？",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0606c12_22",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此人以是因緣得福多不？」",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0606c12_23",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "帝釋天主白佛言：「世尊！",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0606c13_24",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是善男子、善女人，其所得福轉復甚多，算數譬喻所不能及。」",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0606c13_25",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛言：「憍尸迦！",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0606c15_26",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是善男子、善女人，以是因緣得福雖多，不如有人於此般若波羅蜜多，發信解心、發菩提心住菩薩法，以此般若波羅蜜多，書寫經卷受持讀誦，生歡喜心為人演說，或復為人解釋其義，於此正法生清淨心離諸疑惑，轉勸他人使其受持，作如是言：『汝善男子！",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0606c15_27",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此般若波羅蜜多是菩薩道，汝於是中如所宣說應當修學。",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0606c21_28",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是學者乃名得法，即能速證阿耨多羅三藐三菩提，能盡一切諸有情界，普令安住真如實際。』",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0606c22_29",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "憍尸迦！",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0606c25_30",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是善男子、善女人得福甚多。",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0606c25_31",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0606c25_32",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所有阿羅漢果，從是般若波羅蜜多所出生故。",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0606c26_33",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又此善男子、善女人，隨所宣說般若波羅蜜多，即能隨轉；以隨轉故，如其所說即能修學，得先佛法成就阿耨多羅三藐三菩提。",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0606c27_34",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故所有須陀洹、斯陀含、阿那含、阿羅漢、緣覺，及彼如來、應供、正等正覺，皆悉從是般若波羅蜜多出生。",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0606c30_35",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如所出生，如理而得。",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0607a02_36",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，憍尸迦！",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0607a03_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若有善男子、善女人，以滿閻浮提所有眾生，若滿四大洲、若滿小千世界、若滿中千世界、若滿三千大千世界，乃至若滿兢伽沙數三千大千世界所有眾生，普令安住諸緣覺果。",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0607a03_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "憍尸迦！",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0607a07_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於汝意云何，此人以是因緣得福多不？」",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0607a07_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "帝釋天主白佛言：「甚多，世尊！」",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0607a08_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛言：「憍尸迦！",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0607a09_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是善男子、善女人，以是因緣得福雖多，不如有人於此般若波羅蜜多，發信解心、發菩提心住菩薩法，以此般若波羅蜜多，書寫經卷受持讀誦，生歡喜心為人演說，或復為人解釋其義，於此正法生清淨心離諸疑惑，轉勸他人使其受持，作如是言：『汝善男子！",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0607a09_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此般若波羅蜜多是菩薩道，汝於是中如所宣說應當修學。",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0607a15_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是學者乃名得法，即能速證阿耨多羅三藐三菩提，能盡一切諸有情界，普令安住真如實際。』",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0607a16_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "憍尸迦！",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0607a18_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是善男子、善女人得福甚多。",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0607a18_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0607a19_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所有緣覺果，從是般若波羅蜜多所出生故。",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0607a19_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又此善男子、善女人，隨所宣說般若波羅蜜多，即能隨轉；以隨轉故即能修學，得先佛法成就阿耨多羅三藐三菩提。",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0607a20_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故所有須陀洹乃至如來、應供、正等正覺，皆悉從是般若波羅蜜多出生。",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0607a23_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如所出生，如理而得。",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0607a25_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，憍尸迦！",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0607a26_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若滿閻浮提中所有眾生，皆發阿耨多羅三藐三菩提心，若有善男子、善女人，以此般若波羅蜜多書寫經卷，普施一切使其受持。",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0607a26_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不如有人以此般若波羅蜜多，書寫經卷，與一住不退轉菩薩摩訶薩，令其於此般若波羅蜜多，修學相應堅固增長，廣大圓滿成就佛法。",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0607a29_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "憍尸迦！",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0607b03_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當知是善男子、善女人得福甚多。",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0607b03_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0607b04_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此般若波羅蜜多出生阿耨多羅三藐三菩提故。",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0607b04_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "憍尸迦！",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0607b05_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如前所說，若滿閻浮提所有眾生，皆發阿耨多羅三藐三菩提心，且置是數。",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0607b05_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "假使若滿四大洲、若滿小千世界、若滿中千世界、若滿三千大千世界，乃至若滿兢伽沙數三千大千世界所有眾生，皆發阿耨多羅三藐三菩提心。",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0607b07_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若善男子、善女人，以此般若波羅蜜多，書寫經卷，普施一切使其受持。",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0607b10_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "憍尸迦！",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0607b12_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不如有人以此般若波羅蜜多，書寫經卷，與一住不退轉菩薩摩訶薩，令其於此般若波羅蜜多，修學相應堅固增長，廣大圓滿成就佛法。",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0607b12_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "憍尸迦！",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0607b15_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當知是善男子、善女人得福甚多。",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0607b15_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0607b16_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此般若波羅蜜多出生阿耨多羅三藐三菩提故。",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0607b16_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，憍尸迦！",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0607b18_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若滿閻浮提所有眾生，一切皆住不退轉地。",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0607b18_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若有善男子、善女人，以此般若波羅蜜多法門，普為一切解釋其義。",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0607b19_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "憍尸迦！",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0607b20_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於汝意云何，此人以是因緣得福多不？」",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0607b21_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "帝釋天主白佛言：「世尊！",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0607b21_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是善男子、善女人所獲福德，轉復甚多無量無邊，算數譬喻所不能及。」",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0607b22_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛言：「憍尸迦！",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0607b24_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此人以是因緣得福雖多，不如有人為一將證阿耨多羅三藐三菩提者，以此般若波羅蜜多法門解釋其義，當知是人得福甚多。",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0607b24_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "憍尸迦！",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0607b27_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如前所說，滿閻浮提所有眾生，皆住不退轉地，若人普為解釋其義，且置是數。",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0607b27_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "假使若滿四大洲、若滿小千世界、若滿中千世界、若滿三千大千世界，乃至若滿兢伽沙數三千大千世界所有眾生，一切皆住不退轉地。",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0607b29_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若善男子、善女人，以此般若波羅蜜多法門，普為一切解釋其義。",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0607c03_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "憍尸迦！",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0607c04_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於汝意云何，此人以是因緣得福多不？」",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0607c04_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "帝釋天主白佛言：「世尊！",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0607c05_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是善男子、善女人所獲福德無量無邊，算數譬喻所不能及。」",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0607c06_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛言：「憍尸迦！",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0607c07_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此人以是因緣得福雖多，不如有人為一將證阿耨多羅三藐三菩提者，以此般若波羅蜜多法門解釋其義，當知是人得福甚多。",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0607c08_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "憍尸迦！",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0607c10_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩摩訶薩修學是般若波羅蜜多故，速得阿耨多羅三藐三菩提。」",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0607c11_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，帝釋天主白佛言：「世尊！",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0607c13_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩摩訶薩隨轉般若波羅蜜多故，得近阿耨多羅三藐三菩提。",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0607c13_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "隨近阿耨多羅三藐三菩提故，當隨教受般若波羅蜜多。",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0607c15_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如所教受故，隨近一切智。",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0607c16_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故當以飲食、衣服、臥具、醫藥種種供養般若波羅蜜多。",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0607c17_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "隨其所作一切福行，彼獲福德無量無邊。",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0607c18_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0607c19_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "得近阿耨多羅三藐三菩提成就一切智。」",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0607c19_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，尊者須菩提讚帝釋天主言：「善哉，善哉！",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0607c21_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "憍尸迦！",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0607c22_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝善開導諸菩薩摩訶薩，復能護念諸菩薩摩訶薩。",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0607c22_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "憍尸迦！",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0607c23_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛諸弟子皆以阿耨多羅三藐三菩提法護念諸菩薩摩訶薩，令發阿耨多羅三藐三菩提心，令住阿耨多羅三藐三菩提果。",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0607c23_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0607c26_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "過去諸菩薩摩訶薩，皆因學是六波羅蜜多故，發菩提心住菩提果，今佛世尊亦學是六波羅蜜多故得菩提果，未來諸菩薩摩訶薩亦復如是。",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0607c26_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故，憍尸迦！",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0607c29_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若菩薩摩訶薩不學是六波羅蜜多，即不能得阿耨多羅三藐三菩提果。」",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0608a01_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛說佛母出生三法藏般若波羅蜜多經卷第五",
        "from": "T08n0228_005:0608a03_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": false
    }
